al argument and the division of that time among the various issues presented by these cases the executive branch and mccain parties should be permitted to utilizetheir allotted time without regard to the subdivision of the plaintiffs time and subject only to the constraints identified in our july 14 motion respectfully submitted theodore b olson solicitor general counsel of record july 2003
